       "│ (\u001b[38;5;33mEmbedding\u001b[0m)         │                   │            │                   │\n",
       "├─────────────────────┼───────────────────┼────────────┼───────────────────┤\n",
       "│ bidirectional_1     │ (\u001b[38;5;45mNone\u001b[0m, \u001b[38;5;34m512\u001b[0m)       │  \u001b[38;5;34m1,574,912\u001b[0m │ bidirectional[\u001b[38;5;34m0\u001b[0m]… │\n",
       "│ (\u001b[38;5;33mBidirectional\u001b[0m)     │                   │            │                   │\n",
       "├─────────────────────┼───────────────────┼────────────┼───────────────────┤\n",
